track_notes: This route ends at the wooden bench, which has a small open area for activating. There are several intersections with other trails along the way, and the trail signs are a bit ambiguous, so route-finding can be a little tricky.
track_title: One-way, the shortest route from the Jim Whittaker Wilderness Peak Trailhead

track_notes: This route follows the wider trails and might be a better choice on busy days when there are many people on the mountain. Also ends at the wooden bench.
track_title: One way, slightly longer route from the Jim Whittaker Wilderness Peak Trailhead

track_notes: From Sky Country Trailhead (166th Way SE) to KG-132 summit at the end of the trail (wood bench). Round-trip GPS track.
